@FakeTargetApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5067

### Health check
GET {{FakeTargetApi_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Get JWT token (store as @token for /orders)
# @name login
POST {{FakeTargetApi_HostAddress}}/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "testpass"
}

###

### List all products
GET {{FakeTargetApi_HostAddress}}/products
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a product
POST {{FakeTargetApi_HostAddress}}/products
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Widget C",
  "price": 29.99
}

###

### Update a product
PUT {{FakeTargetApi_HostAddress}}/products/2
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Widget C Updated",
  "price": 39.99
}

###

### Delete a product
DELETE {{FakeTargetApi_HostAddress}}/products/2

###

### Get orders (requires Bearer token from /auth/token)
GET {{FakeTargetApi_HostAddress}}/orders
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###

### Get reports (slow — adds ReportsExtraDelayMs on top of global DelayMs)
GET {{FakeTargetApi_HostAddress}}/reports
Accept: application/json

###

### Get external data (flaky — 30% chance of 503 by default)
GET {{FakeTargetApi_HostAddress}}/external-data
Accept: application/json
